* install
** Use a pre-built binary  
  pkg install hs-xmonad  trayer  libghc-xmonad-dev libghc-xmonad-contrib-dev xmobar xcompmgr nitrogen stalonetray moreutils synapse  terminator remmina dmenu dzen rxvt-unicode 

* usage 
 Alt+Q 键盘快捷方式重新加载配置

